---
title: Vercel
---

# Vercel

Vercel provides instant deployments with preview URLs for every pull request.

<Steps>
<Step title="Import your repository">

Go to [vercel.com](https://vercel.com), click **Add New Project**, and import your GitHub repository.

</Step>
<Step title="Configure build settings">

Set the following in the project settings:

| Setting | Value |
|:--------|:------|
| **Build Command** | `curl -fsSL https://oxidoc.dev/install.sh | sh && oxidoc build` |
| **Output Directory** | `dist` |
| **Install Command** | _(leave empty)_ |

</Step>
<Step title="Deploy">

Click **Deploy**. Vercel will build and deploy your site. Every push to `main` triggers a production deploy, and pull requests get preview URLs.

</Step>
</Steps>

<Callout kind="info" title="Build cache">
The install script downloads a pre-built binary, so builds are fast without any compilation step.
</Callout>
